This is Puppet(5.x) agent installer using Ansible  

Currently supports:
 - Ubuntu 16
 - CentOS 7

## How to use

1. Update the host file with server(s) that need to be bootstrapped with Puppet

2. Set package version in group_vars/all.yml [optional]

3. Run Ansible Playbook 

a) For testing environemt run: 
   $ ansible-playbook -i hosts testing.yml -K -k

b) For production environment run: 
   $ ansible-playbook -i hosts production.yml -K -k
